969. Pancake Sorting
     two step:
     1) find the largest element at index i and reverse i+1 elements.
     2) reverse A[0] (the largest) to its position A[largest - 1].
     for each step, adding record to result list.
     
974. Subarray Sums Divisible by K
     if sum[0, i] % K == sum[0, j] % K, sum[i + 1, j] is divisible by by K.
     
